EDAC/highbank: Fix memory leak in highbank_mc_probe()

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.4.231 by commit 8d23f5d25264beb223ee79cdb530b88c237719fc, it was introduced in version v3.6 by commit a1b01edb274518c7da6d69b84e7558c092282aad. For more details please see the references link.
